// services/loveDescriptions.ts

// This data is pre-processed from the user-provided text.
export const loveDescriptions = new Map<string, string>([
  ['1-1', `1a, you are, in many ways, an individual and can be considered a go-getter. Your match with 1b has good prospects because you have a lot in common. All matters considered, you two would get along fairly well with lots of fireworks and sparks to enjoy. However, make sure you discuss what you intend to do with 1b BEFORE you take the lead in any matter, as you might find 1b has other ideas about what you intend to do and what they would rather do. You are both leaders, so make sure you are pointed in the same direction and then go and have some fun together.`],
  ['1-2', `1a, this is an interesting match. It would seem that your interest in 2b is based on something more than pure excitement. There is a difference between you two in that you expect action and spontaneous combustion, whereas 2b is more reserved and would like to pace things out a little. You will have to keep your communication levels up and be patient with 2b. However, if you do and don't rush things, 2b may surprise you now and again with something unexpected.`],
  ['1-3', `1a, the interest you have with 3b is full of potential. You are the one who initiates the ideas, and 3b likes to have fun. Both of you have similar qualities and can really enjoy each other in every aspect. However, just make sure that you don't give away too many of your secrets to 3b until you really get to know them, as they can be quite the chatterbox when excited or upset. So be nice to 3b, and they will be really nice back.`],
  ['1-4', `1a, you do have things in common with 4b, but 4b is more reserved with their emotions on the surface than you are. Your ideas are imaginative and creative, whereas 4b is a little more focused and possibly tends to have a narrow-minded perception of what they want over what you have your designs on. 4b is a little more passionate and romantic compared to you, but 4b is dedicated when things are going smoothly. A word of warning, 1a, be nice to 4b as they have a long memory and can be unforgiving if you rush in too fast and rush away with only your interests being considered. Long nights of passion can endure with 4b, so keep mindful and enjoy the passion.`],
  ['1-5', `1a, this is a great match. You and 5b are both expressive and into action in just about everything you do. At every level, you and 5b can enjoy all the passion and excitement that can be written about. Just make sure you don't exhaust yourselves and lose interest too early in the match. Because you two are similar with your variety of interests, it is good that you both focus on what you want and try to stay on track. 5b has a lot of interests, and their mind is forever seeking new ideas and places to venture. You, 1a, on the other hand, enjoy the new and exciting. Make sure you are open and honest, and keep each other informed, and all should be fun and games for a long time.`],
  ['1-6', `1a, this is an interesting combination as 6b is almost the opposite of you in that you like to take the initiative and lead, and 6b has all the ideas about how things should be done. I have to wonder what it is you find intriguing about 6b, as this relationship will require some tolerance on your part. However, you and 6b can work things through as long as you let 6b feel as if they are in control and pretend it was their idea in the first place. You will receive a lot of love from 6b, but it will be under their rules and timing. To turn them on, simply send all the love messages their way, and they will respond like stroking a cat; careful though, cats can scratch in the blink of an eye if you are not alert.`],
  ['1-7', `1a, this is a cute situation. You are full of energy and vibrancy, but 7b is much more reserved and a deep-thinking person in comparison. However, the ideas you have can attract the mind of 7b and excite them from the inside out. 7b will enjoy your ideas but will always hope that you can perform as well as you talk. Your romantic encounters will be satisfying as long as you tend to the needs of 7b and are not there just for self-indulgence. Appreciate that 7b has a quality nature and is not into the rush-rush ways of life as you are used to. Although you two are different, 7b will like your ideas and support you, so give each other space. When you do come together, make sure you give it all you've got, and 7b will appreciate your genuine passions.`],
  ['1-8', `1a, this is a relationship that is filled with struggles and yet can be full-on too. You have the desire to lead the way, and 8b has the power to lead the way. 8b is strong and decisive about what they want to do, and you are open to opportunity. This is a common denominator, but you may end up pulling away from each other instead of driving ahead in the same direction. Give some thought to setting up some rules with this match, and then you may have some progress. Leave it to chance, and you may find that 8b may leave the party before you realize what has happened. Try as you may on this one, 8b is a handful at any price.`],
  ['1-9', `1a, you and 9b are quite opposite in many ways. You love the new and exciting, whereas 9b enjoys the philanthropic side of life and has more tolerance and compassion. The fire that could burn between the two of you and warm each other's hearts must be managed with understanding, as your interest with 9b may dwindle. 9b has a more wholesome understanding about life and love compared to you. Your passion and interests are intense and fast, so pushing your lust onto 9b, and unless 9b is able to handle it, it may be a little too much of a whirlwind for 9b to handle. One good thing about this match is there is a complementary set of characteristics that can bring many happy hours of love and romance for you two to enjoy.`],
  ['2-1', `2a, the idea of love and a relationship with 1b is a little challenging in one instance and very exciting in another. Your friend 1b has drive and passion and is full of adventurous ideas, whereas you are more subdued and prefer to take your time with activities of the heart. It is true that you can plan and even scheme things with a passion, but this is not always the case, and your association with 1b will test your nerves from time to time. Find the common ground where you both can be satisfied with a loving relationship. However, the common ground may be very small, so you'll have to have tolerance with 1b.`],
  ['2-2', `2a, this is a wonderful and complimentary match. There are always differences in relationships, no matter how alike a couple is, but this is a good one. 2b enjoys the quiet times, the long and interesting discussions by the fireside. They take care of the little things that matter, and this is just what you need. 2a, it is your job to make an approach and find anything that does not fit, fix it, and get on with the job of sharing time with this wonderful match. Every now and then, plan something a little spicy too, as 2b, like you, enjoys playing up, and a surprise at the right time will keep 2b and you happy for a long time.`],
  ['2-3', `2a, you are a conscientious and deeply loving person and need to be treated as such by your partner. However, 3b is a lively and chatty type who wants to swing and sing from the rooftops. 3b is very sensitive, like you, but their sensitivity is expressed outwardly to all who can lend a listening ear. Because you are a more reserved and serious lover, 3b is not the perfect match for you. It would be very wise to make sure you have a good understanding of each other's dreams and aspirations in a relationship before you get serious. The energy 3b has may be too much for you to handle in the long run, so be wise and check 3b out a little more before you become entangled.`],
  ['2-4', `2a, this is a good match. You and 4b are similar in many respects and can work your romantic times around your everyday lives with relative ease. 4b enjoys the loyalty that you can offer, and you enjoy the security that 4b can provide. The only glitch I can see is that you do not discuss matters that are important outside of your private times, and this can tip the balance necessary in a relationship; especially this one. You, 2a, need to talk and wish to discuss the deeper side of your relationship and want to understand your partner's thoughts. But 4b is a little more reserved and finds it difficult to discuss personal and private matters that affect them at deep emotional levels. Work this out, and you can experience a deep and meaningful affair.`],
  ['2-5', `2a, your quiet nature and desire for a partner who understands your need to talk will not truly be found with 5b. 5b is a very active thinker and enjoys a good discussion. 5b likes to have fun, and this will be very evident between the sheets. On the other hand, you love to have a deep and meaningful relationship, and 5b may not be able to accommodate your needs on a long-term basis. 5b will be very good at turning your mind on and enjoying the response they get from you. But all this activity without the required orderly approach you may crave from your partner can be the eventual downfall of this match. Talk things through and then have fun. However, without talk, it is poisonous to this relationship, and it may not otherwise last.`],
  ['2-6', `2a, your interest in 6b has its good points and not-so-good points. You are compatible in many areas and enjoy the responsibility in a relationship that 6b can offer you. On the other hand, 6b can be a little bit tough on you and tell you how you like things to be done. This is great if you enjoy being somewhat submissive in your time together, but true romance can flower if you have common interests at heart and 6b has an understanding of your dreams and desires. 6b can be a great asset to a relationship, and they will enjoy the qualities that you also bring. But you will have to speak up when necessary, or you may never speak up and be ruled by the strong, yet compassionate, characteristics of 6b. Love will be meaningful and deep, and maybe that's the way you'd like it. This is a fair match.`],
  ['2-7', `2a, this is a lovely match and has a lot of potential. Your deep and understanding needs in a relationship are matched by 7b, and 7b also admires and recognizes your qualities. Although you are not the same as one another, 7b has a deep understanding about many things and will not generally talk nonsense. 7b enjoys the quality of life and will make sure their passionate times are also quality-laden. It is important that you two talk; otherwise, you may find you say little for too long, and the passion of your romantic encounters may dwindle as well. All good things need maintenance, and if you keep this up with 7b, your love will flourish.`],
  ['2-8', `2a, I am not sure that you understand what kind of romance 8b has in mind, but it may not be as you anticipate. 8b is a strong person with drive and enthusiasm that leaves others in the dust. 8b has a style of passion unlike any other but also recognizes there is a time and place for it. 2a, you will have to gain respect early on in this relationship if it is to last. Otherwise, 8b will take control, and you will have to follow like a lamb. This may be what you enjoy in a relationship, but if it is not, take heed of what is being said here. Your kind and gentle nature needs to be understood, and you need to talk things through. 8b has no time for the weak and will always take control of the direction things are going. There may be passion at the start that blows you away, but things change, and caution is needed here for this match to make it into the history books.`],
  ['2-9', `2a, there is a lot to be gained from this relationship, and you and 9b should enjoy many happy hours discussing life and love. 9b has very deep and emotional needs from a relationship and will reward their lover with many gifts of appreciation. 2a, you love the finer things in life, and 9b enjoys the meaning of it all. You will have a lifetime of enjoyment from 9b that others will envy. This is not a hot and fiery, passionate affair; no, this is a long-term love connection made by nature herself. As long as all the other components of you and 9b's makeup are checked out for the necessary complements, I see no reason for this not to be one of the better matches available for you.`],
  ['3-1', `3a, this is a magical connection and one of nature's finest matches. You, 3a, are sensitive and a feeling person, and 1b is an exciting and vibrant person to have around. 1b enjoys trying new things to keep love alive and is full of ideas and initiative that you both will cherish. When 1b has a passionate thought, look out, as they will make all the moves to hint and lay clues as to their desires. You, 3a, love the fun and passion that comes with a relationship, and so will probably not take too much convincing to get in the mood. Make sure you both have a good idea about what you want from your relationship and set some plans in place that can make your normal routines in life blend with the more intimate parts of your world, and then get on with it.`],
  ['3-2', `3a, your lively nature and desire for fun are not really matched with 2b, as they are more reserved and prefer a deeper and more philosophical side of life and love. 2b is a person with fine qualities and can see the sense in doing things properly; not quite like you in most cases. You, 3a, are very chatty and loving with a lust for excitement and the thrill of a romp around the bedroom or wherever you feel the need. You have a sensitive nature and appreciate that your mate understands your emotional side. It is not that 2b does not understand you; 2b does. The problem is that 2b does not share the intense excitement you cherish so much. This is not a perfect match, and you should address matters before you enter into a relationship with 2b.`],
  ['3-3', `3a, wow, this could be a hot number for you, and you will experience a lot of common ground with 3b. You are passionate about love and all the feelings and sensations that go with it, and so is 3b. 3b has very similar characteristics to you and will compliment you in most ways. The only thing you should consider is that because you two are so alike, you may find you become bored with each other unless there are other qualities that keep your relationship interesting. It is important also that when you and 3b socialize, you keep some sort of control over your emotions and do not go overboard with festivities. Both of you are easily hurt, and we don't want that to happen with such an exciting match.`],
  ['3-4', `3a, the likelihood of you and 4b having a steaming relationship is few and far between. You see, you, 3a, are exciting and enjoy lots of laughter and a good conversation. Your bedroom antics are not conventional, whereas 4b is a little more conservative when compared to you. 4b will find that a more traditional approach to bedroom antics is more suited to their needs. This does not mean that 4b is a deadhead, no way. It is simply that 4b is more serious and deeply sensitive to their personal feelings, but they become alive now and then, especially after a few drinks to loosen them up, and they will drop their guard and can become the life of the party. If you can tolerate long periods between your lovemaking, then hang in there; otherwise, get out. On a brighter note, 4b will be loyal to you above most others out there.`],
  ['3-5', `3a, this is a good match if ever I saw one. There are moments of intense excitement in store for you, and variety to boot. However, just be a little cautious, as both you and 5b enjoy your bedroom antics, but 5b also enjoys the company of many people. If there is anything to be wary of, it is that you and 5b are very clear about your relationship, and that they do not get the chance to spend too much time with other possible relationships that could interfere with your own. This should be evident when you notice how much fun you have with 5b and how easy it was to get along with them in the initial stages of your relationship, that is if you have already started it. A great match, just be cautious.`],
  ['3-6', `3a, this is a complimentary match, and many good times can come from this association. 6b enjoys the fun and family matters and likes the energy you can put into a relationship to keep it light and fluffy. 6b will ensure the home and bedroom are kept clean and pretty, just how you like it too. You, 3a, will bring the fun and excitement into this relationship, and 6b will set the boundaries. This is not a bad thing, it is quite complimentary as mentioned above, and you two should enjoy some lovely times together. Have fun, because this match can work well if you make it work well.`],
  ['3-7', `3a, I have to wonder what it is about 7b that you find interesting. 7b is a reserved person with a great deal of inner activity going on that most people never see. They are deep thinkers and need their time to sit and think, often on their own without interruption. However, there may be qualities you enjoy with 7b, but they will never permit you to fully experience the lust and passion you often crave just for the fun of it. This relationship can work, but it will require that you tone down a lot and that 7b tones up a lot. Then there is the communication; you are light and fluffy with a good joke or two, 7b likes the more serious side of life and may prefer to study worms. This relationship can work with work and tolerance, though. Good luck.`],
  ['3-8', `3a, this is an interesting combination because you are alive and enjoy the excitement of life, whereas 8b has a more serious expectation out of life and love affairs. You may feel a little subordinated by the power and authority that 8b imposes on you, and so I would suggest you question your intentions as far as getting serious with 8b is concerned. 8b has a lot of good qualities, but they are more designed for the serious types, and I feel you are more of the fun and games type. If you do, however, get into bed with 8b, I can see initial exciting times turn into fewer and farther-apart antics as time goes by. If this is not your style, consider another match.`],
  ['3-9', `3a, this is a nice match as you bring color and fun into the relationship, and 9b brings in the romance and all that is lovely. 9b has a quality and an appreciation about love and life, you have an appreciation about enjoying life in general. This is complementary in itself, but it is good that you and 9b discuss your personal needs early in the piece, as you will find that 9b is probably more than willing to make your relationship a long-term one. You, 3a, in turn, should make sure that you do not embarrass your devoted 9b when you socialize, as you can easily become quite festive compared to 9b. So, if you keep your wits about you and communicate well with 9b, I can see a lovely and warm relationship develop that will be the envy of many people.`],
  ['4-1', `4a, your idea of love and relationships is structured to some extent, but the ideas 1b has about how things should be may make you feel a little out of sorts at times. It's not that you and 1b cannot get along; quite the opposite. Simply put, you have an idea of how loving and romance should work, but 1b has all sorts of ideas, and this may have you working overtime on some passionate encounters. Talk to 1b and tell them how you think things should be in your time together, and if they are listening, they will experience many hours of heated love with you and a loyalty that will be long-lasting. This is a fair match, but make sure you are not the one who gets hurt, which is possible if you have not laid out the ground rules from the very start.`],
  ['4-2', `4a, this is a compatible match between you and 2b. 4a, you seek loyalty and understanding from a friend or partner, and this comes very close with 2b. 2b is a little quiet at times but loves to talk things through with regard to problems and philosophies. Although this is a general statement about 2b, there is another side to their nature that can be disturbing if 2b has their feathers ruffled and feels a little revengeful. 2b enjoys art, music, and history to some degree, and these qualities may match your outlook on life as well. As far as romance goes, this is not a fiery and ongoing passionate affair but more gentle and long-term with loyalty and stability. Both of you will have to talk to overcome any problems; otherwise, the relationship may be doomed.`],
  ['4-3', `4a, this relationship mix is a little like oil and water. You are sensitive and reserved, with your ability to express your feelings, and 3b is a chatterbox who enjoys discussing everything. 3b is a little sensitive to what is going on around them and can become quite hurt if talked about or if they hear degrading comments about their person, hence some matters will need to be opened up often to override problems. This may be a challenge for you. This raises the point about passion. Although you will enjoy the energy 3b can deliver, it may end up being more overpowering than you can handle over time. Have fun with 3b in the interim and see how things pan out.`],
  ['4-4', `4a, when it comes to a perfect match, this is it. Although you and 4b are well suited personality-wise, you both have the problem to overcome about talking things out when difficulties arise. The common factors of loyalty, deep commitment, romantic passion, and planning your lives are all there and ready for picking; however, as you two are so similar, you may find there is nothing new and exciting going on. The answer to this hurdle is to make your personal life spicy now and then with a little adventure mixed with a little festive socializing. Once 4b has dropped their protective shield, they are hot potatoes and a ball of fun; the same applies to you in this instance. Make this work by planning and discussing, and things will run like clockwork.`],
  ['4-5', `4a, there are some aspects of 5b that are similar to you, but there are also many that are different. 5b is a person who enjoys the company of lots of people and can change direction at the drop of a hat. You, on the other hand, may find it difficult to keep up with 5b, and so you will have to evaluate whether or not this is worth pursuing. The hot times you can have with 5b will be well received, but there will also be many times that require you to change your ways to make this romance a long-term relationship. One of these qualities you may have difficulties with is loyalty. Sometimes 5b has it, and other times not. Measure this relationship with kid gloves so you don't get hurt.`],
  ['4-6', `4a, here is a lovely match with so many areas that complement each other. You love the idea of loyalty, responsibility, deep love, and passion, and 6b has all those qualities to offer you too. The only challenge I see is that you and 6b need to communicate clearly about everything and plan your future right from the start. This will make both of you feel very secure, and the chances are you will have many happy times together. Although you may find at times that 6b can be a little bit bossy, this is okay as long as you can see their point. The same goes for 6b as it does for you, 4a. 6b has to appreciate your side of things as well, and if they do, you can enjoy a long and loving relationship.`],
  ['4-7', `4a, linking up with 7b can be a good thing, even productive. You and 7b have a lot in common, as both of you are very deep people. This is a good start to any relationship, but make sure you keep open communication; otherwise, you, 4a, will become reclusive and oversensitive and may shy away from the obvious question 7b will ask, "What's wrong?" To this, you will probably say, "Oh, nothing." So before things get to that point and you miss out on the excitement this relationship can bring, keep everything in the open and enjoy soft romantic dinners, a glass of wine, and romance that could make Romeo envious.`],
  ['4-8', `4a, this is an interesting match if ever I saw one. You and 8b have similar qualities and interests. 8b likes to get involved with business and making money, and you like to spend it, sometimes wisely and sometimes not. As long as you and 8b are working toward a good cause, you and 8b can have a very positive romance and a long-term relationship. The big challenge will be that you and 8b can be as stubborn as anything, so it is advisable that you take the time to assess everything and place your cards on the table so you both know where you stand and can appreciate one another's gifts, talents, and personal appreciation. Love in this match will be deep and lasting, but a lot of consideration must be given to each other's perspectives.`],
  ['4-9', `4a, I have to wonder what it is you are looking for in this relationship, unless it has to do with your appreciation of other qualities that 9b has apart from your common interests. 9b enjoys love and honesty in life and wants to feel the warmth of humanity and nature in every respect. You, 4a, have a more reserved nature and do not express your ideas and feelings outwardly enough because you are so sensitive about personal matters. You like to get on with things, and 9b wants to get involved with all those that need help. This could cost you a lot of money in the long run. However, loyalty is a common thread between both of you, and maybe this is what can make this match work. Good luck.`],
  ['5-1', `5a, this is an exciting relationship connection. You are both into variety and can dream up many happy hours of fun and frivolity. But all this excitement can be short-lived if you rush things too fast and lose the long-term benefits that can come out of such a match. You love change, and 1b enjoys the new and exciting, so with all this activity going on, plan some time for eating and sleeping; it will help and be a necessary fact of life. After things settle down and the heat is out of the fire, find the time to talk and plan a little. You have a wonderful connection, and any future based on passion and emotions will be short-lived because of instability and a lack of security. Love and live, but be sure to make plans.`],
  ['5-2', `5a, this is not really a perfect match with you and 2b, as your energy levels and love of variety do not match the quiet pace and principles of doing things methodically as does 2b. This can cause a rift between you two because of the very dissimilar nature you have with each other. This does not mean to say it cannot work, but it does indicate there will be times, and possibly many of them, when you will be at odds with one another due to your different ideas and ideals. 5a, you need variety, action, and a person who enjoys doing lots of stuff. 2b enjoys the quiet side of life, and therefore your interests are few in common and many in dissimilarities. Sorry about the big words, but I would suggest more thought be put into this match before any commitments are made.`],
  ['5-3', `5a, a good match can be the outcome of any relationship you have with 3b. They are funny and full of spirit, figuratively speaking. However, both of you can become overly festive and socialize to the limit and forget the events you got up to overnight. This may be fun but at the same time may not indicate a solid and long-term healthy relationship will follow. The best part of this match between you and 3b is the happiness that can be born of it. The worst scenario is that you can easily find fun and games with other people as well. So my advice is to have fun but also take responsibility in this relationship and tango so that you have a long-term association rather than a short-term fling.`],
  ['5-4', `5a, there are good points and not-so-good points to this relationship. The good points are that you have some technical points about life and work in common, but the other side of the coin is that you may enjoy one another's company now and then on personal levels, but not on others, most others! When talking about relationships, love, and passion are the focus in the initial stages; you and 4b may have sparks flying initially, but I fear that there will be challenges after a short period of time. Give it a go, but if the going gets rough, just go. Good luck.`],
  ['5-5', `5a, this is a very exciting relationship, and there are a lot of prospects that can be considered in a variety of aspects between the two of you. You love fun, excitement, and change in your routines... so does 5b. The biggest problem that can arise in this affair is that you may both decide you have become bored with each other and need a change from one another. That's bad judgment on both your accounts. Do the right thing and enjoy the variety you both love so much, from one another. Then you and 5b can enjoy many years of love and passion that will be the envy of many. A great match; just don't make the mistake of bungling it.`],
  ['5-6', `5a, putting it lightly, this is a match that does not fit with any degree of comfort. 5b is like chalk and you are like cheese. 5a, you like the fun and variety in life, and 6b wants things in order and as they should be, according to the laws and ways of 6b. This relationship will stifle and strangle you in the long run, so make every effort to check things through before you decide that this relationship is worth pursuing. 6b is house-proud and likes things in an organized fashion. If you decide to remain as you are, you may find you are on the wrong end of 6b's tongue on several occasions, and you may enjoy time away from 6b more than in the bedroom with 6b. I hope you got the message here. However, a final note; there may be other factors that bring your personalities and nature together. This being so, this could be a fabulous affair.`],
  ['5-7', `5a, you are an exciting and fun-filled person. 7b is not quite your kettle of fish. 7b enjoys reading and researching or simply asking questions to find out why you do this and why you don't do that instead. After a time, you may discover that the qualities of 7b are not really suited to your personality type. 7b needs someone to discover the hidden side of life, to reach the deepest secrets there are in life and people. This should scare the hell out of you as you will be caught out every time and you may not enjoy that prospect. I suggest you find another person to enjoy your private life with and give 7b a lot of consideration before you jump in blind.`],
  ['5-8', `5a, I can imagine you may be fascinated with some of the qualities that 8b has, but be warned, 8b is not a person to mess around with as they can be the caring individual and the executioner as well if you muck them about. 8b enjoys a proper lifestyle with lots of formalities. You 5a, on the other hand, enjoy a variety of interests, and this can make 8b feel very unstable. Unless you are endowed with the qualities that are found elsewhere in your personality that are common ground to 8b, be cautioned, this is like trying to land a 15-foot great white shark with light fishing tackle in a rubber dinghy. Caution on this one, 5a. Good luck.`],
  ['5-9', `5a, I have to wonder what it is you hope to achieve in a relationship with 9b. 9b is a deep and passionate lover of life and all that is good and fair, you, on the other hand, love life and want to enjoy as much of it as possible. I don't mean to be so harsh on you; it is just that you enjoy variety and need things to be happening around you, whereas 9b likes to settle into a quiet and comfortable pace of life that does not require rushing about like a blowfly. 9b is passionate and loves to love everyone at platonic levels; however, 9b does have time for that special someone. You need a person with more interest in jumping off cliffs to get thrills, and 9b may disappoint you with their reservations. 5a, you need a live fish so go and catch that tiger by the tail and hang on for the ride.`],
  ['6-1', `6a, you are so idealistic about the love and passion you desire from and are willing to give to a perfect partner; this one, 1b, has all the trademarks of one who will deliver the goods in a relationship, but their ideas are more radical and possibly at times, too much to contend with. 1b is very interested in making love and will make the time for it, whereas you are more interested in security, loyalty, and being looked after with all the nice things in life. Don't be too bossy with 1b as they are sensitive to being told what to do and you are, in some ways, a dictator of how things should be done for the benefit of the relationship. You'll love 1b for the passion 1b can deliver, and on the other hand, 6a, 1b will enjoy the emotional warmth you have to offer. This is a challenging relationship and needs much maintenance.`],
  ['6-2', `6a, this could be a good match indeed. Your interest with 2b, who is a gentle soul with a lot of patience and understanding, can have long-term rewards. This is good as far as you are concerned because 2b will have a great deal of understanding for you and your ways. Love in this relationship will be deep and meaningful. This does not mean there will be only slow and romantic times, but more often than not, this match is one that is harmonious rather than chasing each other naked around the park for fun. You are serious and expect a lot from those you love; 2b is more reserved and will see your reasoning better than most. Once again, a nice match to enjoy.`],
  ['6-3', `6a, there are some good points and not-so-good points in this relationship. The good ones are that you and 3b have a common emotional makeup and both of you appreciate the arts and music. It is not quite the same when it comes to control over one's emotions, however, and you may find that 3b is a little oversensitive and reactive to some of the things you say that are directed at 3b. You like things in some form of order and 3b likes all sorts of things in all sorts of ways; this includes the passionate times and the romance that you two can truly enjoy as well. As long as you think before you speak to 3b and understand that 3b will react rather than respond to what you say or suggest, you should get along quite amicably. Just know that you are the boss, and 3b will voice their opinion without thought at times.`],
  ['6-4', `6a, this is a good match in the making but will need some work to ensure all is well and you are both heading in the same direction. You like to have things in order and as they should be, whereas 4b likes to do things in a certain way and can feel frustrated if things have to change to suit your needs. 4b is a loyal and deep lover, so are you, but 4b has a difficult time expressing their true feelings and may clam up when you start to dictate or put pressure on 4b, even though you may feel that you aren't. The long-term possibilities with you two are good, but communication and understanding are very important in this match. Money and love will grow in this personality mix, so give it a go and be careful of the other's feelings.`],
  ['6-5', `6a, this is not quite the perfect matchmaker's match. No! What we have here is you, a person who likes things done in a certain way that works for everybody, and then there's 5b who enjoys a variety of interests and likes to change things like routines, etc., about from time to time. This will probably annoy you. The good things are the fun times that 5b can offer, including the bedroom and the social life, but when it comes down to formalities and basics, 5b will frustrate you no end. 6a, your responsible and often mature nature, is abused by the carefree attitude of 5b at times, and unless you are prepared to tolerate this quality for whatever reason, think twice about a serious and long-term relationship with this person.`],
  ['6-6', `6a, you have a natural connection with 6b and things can really work for both of you in a long-term relationship. There are, however, serious pointers that must be considered before you go too far down the track. Both of you like to control the reins, and this may cause a conflict of interests. Yes indeed you and 6b can enjoy the full embrace of a long and passionate relationship, but once again, there will be two bosses in this household and one of you will have to relinquish their control to the other that may meet with distaste. If you and 6b can discuss very decisively what has to be done and who has the responsibility over whatever areas of your lives, things should work out on all levels in a positive manner.`],
  ['6-7', `6a, this relationship has potential to work or to be very destructive depending on how you look at it and approach life on other levels than just pure love. Between you two, love can be mad and passionate with fireworks and excitement. However, if there is a difference of opinion with regard to other matters, look out, as there can be fireworks and devastation when things don't go quite according to plan. Both you and 7b have different ways of thinking and living. If you do not sort this out very early in the piece, expect there to be problems and ongoing difficulties for the rest of your lives. It can work, but it requires your devotion and understanding.`],
  ['6-8', `6a, this combination has huge potential, as there are the rewards of love and money in one package on offer. You have the drive and responsibility to get ahead and make your home a happy one full of love and family matters, and 8b has the drive and determination to get the job done and organize the ship at any cost. Both of you are determined with a passion, and this also applies to the bedroom. However, there is a time and place for everything, and 8b will make this known early on in the relationship. You, 6a, on the other hand, will make sure that 8b enjoys the loving side of your passionate nature and will make every effort to ensure that those long and personal times starting with candlelit dinners are not forgotten. A good match, so keep your boxing gloves hidden from each other and always at hand to protect this wonderful nest egg from invaders.`],
  ['6-9', `6a, this is a lovely combination for a relationship. You both enjoy the idea of a home and family, and you, 6a, can make sure it happens. 9b has the compassion to make sure all is well and keep the relationship on an even keel, and this is excellent as long as there are no selfish tendencies allowed to pop up like mushrooms in the dark. All that is warm and beautiful can emanate from your being together. You have a closeness that others would envy, so work at this relationship, and you will spend many happy years in love, around the home, and especially during those intimate nights, cuddled up in one another's arms.`],
  ['7-1', `7a, there are good points and interesting aspects in this match between you and 1b. Both of you like things to be done your own way, and when you're pointed in the same direction, the thrill of engagement enters the arena, allowing you to enjoy each other's passion to the limit. 1b has ideas and will likely love to try different things, whereas you feel the need to think things through a little more before leaping into something that isn't quite you. This doesn't mean you're mismatched; it means that when you and 1b are thinking along the same lines, there's fire in the hole, and a great deal of heat can be generated from your passions.`],
  ['7-2', `7a, this is a nice combination. You and 2b have a lot in common and can probably spend a great deal of time together sharing and experiencing wonderful thoughts and activities. 7a, you enjoy quality time with people, and this is where 2b fits in nicely. 2b has understanding and patience above most others, and the similarities between the two of you cover a wide range of subjects. Romance and passion can be equally shared, and you may spend many nights and weekends enjoying each other's company. The only downfall could be that you do not open up to one another for whatever reason, and this will cause one or both of you to hide inside your shells like hermit crabs. Keep your communication open, and this relationship will work wonders.`],
  ['7-3', `7a, you will probably enjoy the bright, colorful nature of 3b, and 3b will enjoy the quality that you emanate through your personality. As nice as these factors are, they are not compatible when you take the formal position of relationships into consideration. You have such a deep nature, 7a, and 3b are all chatty and enjoy the great outdoors. This may, and probably will be the cause of conflict between you two should you decide that you want to make a go of anything in the form of a long-term tie-up. This is not to say that you do not enjoy similar activities as 3b, but it does indicate that you and 3b will eventually see the differences between you, and things may just naturally come to an emotional end. Don't do this to yourself, 7a; it's not worth it.`],
  ['7-4', `7a, although this is not quite the perfect match, there are signs that this relationship with 4b has the potential to be quite favorable. You are a deep thinker, 7a, and 4b is simply deep. 4b has a tendency to become oversensitive at times, and you will have to be careful how you go about extracting information from them to ease their burden, or else they may just clam up altogether. The both of you enjoy deep love, and this is the one aspect that I can promise can come from this tie. Loyalty and understanding each other are the qualities of this relationship, but be warned, stupidity brings its own punishment. Be good to each other.`],
  ['7-5', `7a, this is a challenging relationship, to say the least. 5b has such a bright personality and has many skills and interests that will hold your focus... for a time. The problem with 5b is that they are into living life in so many different areas that you will need to constantly analyze what they are into now and up to next. 5b will enjoy your qualities, but they will soon become bored with the way you want things. You are so analytical and sometimes a little too concerned with seeking answers that 5b will prefer to avoid your presence. This relationship is a mixed bag of sweets and not really in your best interests. Just like you do best, have a lot of time to think about this relationship before you dive in blindly.`],
  ['7-6', `7a, there is a saying you may have heard: 6's and 7's. This is a relationship match that needs a lot of thought because the differences between the two of you are many, yet the desire for a common lifestyle is also present. You, 7a, see the need to improve or perfect some areas of 6b's life, whereas 6b has a tendency to love passionately but demand a standard of living that suits their way of thinking, not necessarily matching yours. This can, and probably will, create conflicts of interest. The funny thing is, the relationship you and 6b may enjoy is often found in others with similar make-up to what the two of you have or are contemplating. The only response I can offer you is that sometimes, opposites attract, and you and 6b are just that. Give it a careful go, but watch your step.`],
  ['7-7', `7a, this is a great match in some ways but can be a challenge in another. The points to look forward to are that you and 7b have a lot in common. You both like the deep nature of each other, the times to talk about the weird and wonderful, planning those interesting nights, and general qualities of life that are a little different from most. On the other hand, you both can be so deep and reserved that there will be no talking, and without communication, all sorts of problems can arise. To avoid any challenges, keep both your noses clean and avoid becoming involved in trying to help other people with problems, as you may find that you collect the rotten sods of society and they will destroy anything you have gained. Love each other, but don't overspend.`],
  ['7-8', `7a, this is not quite the bond that was intended to be blessed with longevity and harmony. You, 7a, are too sensitive for the strong will and direct nature of 8b. There may be qualities the two of you have in common, but they are few and far between, and you will find after a short time that 8b has a personality that rubs you the wrong way and can hurt your feelings, as they see things from a different angle than you do. 8b is an organizer, a direct, get-up-and-go person who has no time for woozy people. This being the case, you may find yourself at the end of a pointed finger and a tongue-lashing you don't appreciate at all. So, 7a, be very careful with this one as it is not a perfect match made in heaven.`],
  ['7-9', `7a, to all intents and purposes, this is a congenial match that has the potential to work quite well. 9b is a gentle and wise person having a tendency to care about many things in life and an understanding similar to you about the purpose behind it all. Your passionate times will be filled with gentle loving and wrapped up in purple and red ribbons, and laced with loyalty. Sounds nice, don't you think? On the negative side, 9b can be a little selfish, and you can be a little quiet, hiding from your partner in deep thought. It is best to talk about every issue between you and to make sure there is understanding and that you are not just giving lip service to 9b, as you, 7a, can be a little deceitful if you are not honest with yourself first and foremost. Be good to each other.`],
  ['8-1', `8a, you are a strong and determined lover with a drive that can move mountains, but there is a time and place for everything, and this is not quite how 1b operates in the world of love. 1b enjoys spontaneity and likes to try this and that, and you are more serious. Although you are one to be reckoned with in the bedroom, as you are a very serious lover, there is still a time and place for everything in your life, and this is not the way that 1b sees how things should be done. By all means, test the waters with 1b, but also test the future potential with them. If you feel there may be a few challenges early on, have fun for now, but don't get too serious, or the glue may fall from the cracks and the wails of romance may quickly fade into rubble.`],
  ['8-2', `8a, there are good points and not-so-good points with this match, mostly difficult ones, I have to admit. 2b has a gentle nature and is more slowly paced when compared to you. They have a nice nature and are attentive to every detail, which can be nice when you are in an intimate situation. However, this is not your style in the long run, is it, 8a? You have a lot of other things to consider than just the bedroom. There is a time and place for everything, and that's the nature of the beast, as far as you are concerned, anyway. So, for a good match, I advise that you enjoy what you can from 2b and be kind to them, but look elsewhere for a better match that is more suited to your nature. Otherwise, good luck!`],
  ['8-3', `8a, the probability that you will hang on to this relationship is not the best. 3b is a lively and colorful person who enjoys life to the fullest and is a little like a butterfly on heat. You, on the other hand, are a more sensible person who enjoys getting down to business and working hard to achieve the rewards you know you deserve out of life. You may find that 3b is an enjoyable character to have for those intimate times, but their lack of determination and drive on the more serious issues you believe in may bring down the curtain on this relationship. Enjoy yourself while it lasts and be kind to your sensitive friend 3b.`],
  ['8-4', `8a, many of the characteristics that you and 4b have are similar and therefore show promise in this relationship should it go ahead. 4b has a hardworking nature and is loyal and serious about what they do. 4b will also be a lot of fun when socializing, especially after they have loosened up with a few drinks. Just be watchful over 4b as they have a tendency to go too far at this point and can become an embarrassment to you. Although you, 8a, are considered more formal than 4b, you can also be a devil if you want to be and can kick your heels up too. Therefore, some of the characteristics between you two are similar, and some are dangerous. Be good to each other, have fun, mind your manners, and don't argue, as you will both lose in the end.`],
  ['8-5', `8a, this is a relationship that will require your full attention if you are to make it last with 5b. You see, 5b is a quick-thinking and energetic person who has no real grounding and stickability with much of their life's activities. This is not bad; it just is not in compliance with your nature. You enjoy sensible people with a purpose, and oftentimes 5b has quite the opposite perspective and therefore will cause you grief with their unreliability. 5b has a lot of good qualities and will be a fun person to have around when you are feeling frisky, but this is not really a perfect match, so be cautious and look below the surface with what 5b may be telling you, as it may not be quite as they are saying.`],
  ['8-6', `8a, there is power and potential in this combination. You and 6b have a lot in common, even your ideals and dreams are similar. Your passion and intimate times will be fulfilling, and there is a great deal of loyalty and family bonding that will come from such a match. The downside holds a few bumps for you and 6b. Be careful that you do not get stuck over silly arguments or points that you and 6b will not budge from; it is the determined nature you both have that can cause grief if there is to be any. 6b is a little more compassionate with family and friends, where you are more direct and unmoving. When you are really upset, you may not express your thoughts until you are ready to. This is not healthy either, so get talking and make sure you both have an agreement to keep the peace as best you can, and all will be well for a long time.`],
  ['8-7', `8a, a match made in heaven this is not. You are too strong and determined for 7b, and they are too quiet and methodical over some issues when compared to you. They have some good qualities and are very wise in many respects, but you, 8a, are more concerned with getting the job done at any cost. When it comes to passion and love, 7b is deep and wants a meaningful relationship, while you want to get it done and get on with it. So, there are not many areas that you and 7b have in common in a relationship format. It would be best for you to keep this match light and fluffy, if you can handle it, and then move on. Otherwise, wish you good luck, as you may need it.`],
  ['8-8', `8a, this is a powerful relationship mix. You have so much in common with 8b, and 8b will have a great deal of respect for you. This is great! When it comes to passion and romance, you both enjoy planning time together, and as long as this happens, and at the right time, you will be content to maintain a long-term and prosperous relationship with 8b for many years. However, be considerate of each other when there is a difference of opinion, as both of you can be so stubborn and rigid in your principles and ways of thinking that your relationship can become a battlefield if you are ignorant of the psychological makeup each of you has.`],
  ['8-9', `8a, your idea of love and romance is slightly off-center compared to 9b's. 9b enjoys the wholesome aspects of life and love and has a great deal of compassion for many people and the way things should be done. You, on the other hand, 8a, are a bit more critical of people and how things should be done when compared to 9b. This may raise some difficulties between you two and cause any long-term prospects to disappear in a puff of smoke. Although there are many differences between you, it will have to be that you make the decisions, 8a, and 9b will have to follow your pointers. If you find that 9b is not happy with this arrangement, you can be fairly sure that what may have started out as a romantic encounter will end in a parting of the ways, unless you both can work things through with great effort, especially on your part, 8a.`],
  ['9-1', `9a, you are so compassionate and loving. This is all you ask of your lovers, to love you the same in return. The way in which 1b will love you is with fire and passion. 1b is a driver who takes control of the throttle and initiates the passion in your heart. You'll have to hold back a little and discuss some points, or 1b may make the moves before you have a chance to understand what's happening. If you love to be swept off your feet with an energetic lover, this is for you; if you are more reserved, hang onto your hat or tell them that a platonic relationship feels best for you. Your choice!`],
  ['9-2', `9a, this is a sweet match and one that has long-term prospects because of the understanding you both have for each other and the world at large. 9a, you have care and consideration with people and have a good understanding about honesty and fair play. 2b has many good qualities, and patience and consideration are but two of them. Together, you and 2b can go a long way in life and love. The only thing to watch out for, 9a, is that you do not become too self-centered and concerned about others so much that you, on your own volition, do too much for others and not enough for 2b; and in the same light, 2b should be aware that they do not become sulky and withdrawn from life. As long as you both understand your downfalls, you should enjoy a long and loving relationship. Good on you.`],
  ['9-3', `9a, there are some good times in this relationship and there are some scratchy times if you are not careful too. 9a, you are caring and considerate and love the arts. 3b is fun and colorful and enjoys artistic-type stuff too. The biggest difference between the two of you is that 3b is far more outgoing than you, and on many levels, more sensitive when exposed to harsh words. I know you are a very understanding person, 9a, and you may have to be this way when 3b is under pressure, but on the same note, let 3b know when they are going overboard with their very expressive personality, and this is especially so when they have had a few drinks at social events. Otherwise, this is a congenial relationship with potential.`],
  ['9-4', `9a, an unusual combination here with you and 4b. You are compassionate and understanding and have a more gentle approach to life, business, and love when compared to 4b. 4b has a down-to-earth approach to life and can focus on what they are doing, not noticing other wonderful things that are happening around them. This is where you will differ, and you may find that after a time, 4b will become a little distant unless there is a high communication level established between the two of you. The good thing about 4b is that they are loyal and believe in established relationships. However, once hurt, they are deeply affected and may not be as forgiving as you are, so watch for this, 9a, or irreparable damage may be done.`],
  ['9-5', `9a, this is a fascinating relationship mix if ever there was one. Your tolerance for the overactive and often non-stick-ability that 5b has may be too much for you to handle at times. You love all that is right and proper, whereas 5b enjoys a bit of this and that and then they'll change their mind and do something else. This can be very challenging indeed. There are the fun times that 5b can bring into a relationship, and they will be very adventurous in those intimate times, but you need some real stability and long-term commitment to make you feel that you are able to go somewhere with 5b. Yes, 9a, you are tolerant and understanding, but there is a lot more required in this match. You may need more than good luck; however, good luck!`],
  ['9-6', `9a, luck and good times are with you in this relationship as both you and 6b have similar understanding and compassion with each other and your fellow associates and family. You may find that 6b is a little bossy at times even though they mean well, and 6b has a lot of drive and quality that you will enjoy in a relationship. Passion and long-term love are assured with this match made in heaven, but be warned about any self-indulgent measures either of you have as this will be your downfall. Of all the matched couples there are in this world, there are not many that can top this one. Be kind to each other, be loyal, and your love will mature and grow continually. What a nice story to hear.`],
  ['9-7', `9a, what you have here is an interesting match and one that will bring many good times for the both of you. 7b is a deep and understanding person, like you in many ways. 7b enjoys the quality of life even though you only go without if the situation calls for it. 9a, I know that honesty and the depth of human nature appeal to you, and 7b can provide this for you, but take heed. 7b may be all that you are looking for in a relationship, but they can become withdrawn and devious if they are mistreated. So it is really important that you watch for this so that you are not caught off guard by the slow decline of 7b who may become a recluse and hide away from others and then you. You are a natural clairvoyant, 9a, so keep your antenna up and be.`],
  ['9-8', `9a, there are two sides to this relationship, yours and theirs. 9a, you are compassionate and caring and have a lot of time and consideration for other people. 8b is not like this most of the time, and therefore you may be faced with battles that you will not win with 8b. 8b has qualities of drive and determination that will leave most people in their dust as they get on with the job at hand and anything else they set their sights on. A relationship with you two will be very complicated and not one that I would recommend without you really getting to know 8b as much as you possibly can about them. Due to the differences between you, you may be left in the cold and not enjoying the loving and caring qualities you so desperately need in your life, sorry.`],
  ['9-9', `9a, this is a lovely combination if ever there was one. You and 9b have so much in common and you really appreciate the views about life that 9b openly expresses. When two people have so much to offer others and each other, love and passion will flourish and you can go a long way together. However, there are matters that need to be addressed. Make sure that aside from all the love and passion you two share, there needs to be tight control over finances and how much time and effort you give to other people who will call upon your help. By giving too much of yourselves to others' needs, you may cause deterioration with the good there is in yours and 9b's life and love, and this is not a good thing. You and 9b should focus on each other first and then see what you can do for others. Love one another, your family, and lastly heed to the call of the needy.`],
]);
